com.microsoft.azure.management.sql

Class ElasticPoolOperationsImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.management.sql.ElasticPoolOperationsImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ElasticPoolOperations, ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>

    public class ElasticPoolOperationsImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>, ElasticPoolOperations
    Represents all the operations for operating on Azure SQL Database Elastic Pools. Contains operations to: Create, Retrieve, Update, and Delete.

        nameFilter - Required. The filter to apply on the name of the metrics.
        timeGrain - Required. The time granularity of the metric to retrieve.
        startTime - Required. The start time for the interval.
        endTime - Required. The end time for the interval.
        Returns:
        Represents Azure SQL Database Elastic Pool metrics.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - Signals that an I/O exception of some sort has occurred. This class is the general class of exceptions produced by failed or interrupted I/O operations.
        ServiceException - Thrown if an unexpected response is found.
